data.description: ***NEW PRICE*** Vacant and can show anytime! Living in a PENTHOUSE unit at Laketown Wharf is amazing! The views of the GULF of MEXICO are breathtaking. This unit sits above the other beachfront condos across the street and the views are incredible. This is a personal residence and not a rental unit. It has upgrades to make this a great lasting unit. The HVAC & HOT WATER TANK are NEW, The lighting has been upgraded, The unit comes fully furnished and move in ready! Includes New ''Poly-wood Type'' Patio Furniture and a lounging bed on the balcony! EVERYTHING in the unit conveys! This could be an extremely profitable rental unit from day one., but cozy enough to be your private residence. All Decor, Artwork and Decorations remain too. Leather couch and recliner, Bed linens, quilts and window treatments remain. There are 2 large bedrooms and a (bunk room/3rd bedroom). Master bath suite has walk-in glassed-in shower and separate soaking tub, double vanities and separate toilet area. Guest bath is a full size, single vanity, toilet and shower.The kitchen boasts all Stainless steel appliances and painted cabinets with granite countertops, beautiful subway tile backsplash too! Laketown Wharf COA dues include everything but power. Insurance, Cable, Internet, Water, GarbageSome of the property amenities include: 5-pools, A 2-story gym, pickleball court,convention center, restaurants, Bar, mail room and boardwalks.
